Portugal Wins European Union Approval for $110.8 Billion in Financial Aid

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-05-16T16:42:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/portugal-wins-european-union-approval-for-110-8-billion-in-financial-aid.html
European Union finance ministers
cleared the way for  Portugal  to receive 78 billion euros in aid,
making it the third euro country to fall back on official loans.  The endorsement came at a meeting of EU finance ministers
in Brussels today, European Commission economics spokesman
 Amadeu Altafaj  said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Neuger at 
